Up to now we have one directory bmnroot/zdc for 3 calorimeters:

 ZDC - old calo without hole, 104 modules 
 FHCal - new calo with hole, 54 modules
 neutron ZDC (nZDC) - new calo without hole, 36 modules

To work with new calorimeters FHCal/nZDC:

cd bmnroot/zdc

After bmnroot installation in derectory bmnroot/zdc one has files 
BmnZdc.h, BmnZdc.cxx, BmnZdcPoint.h, BmnZdcPoint.cxx 
for working with old ZDC

To work with new FHCal/nZDC:

cp BmnZdcPoint_FHCal.h BmnZdcPoint.h
cp BmnZdcPoint_FHCal.cxx BmnZdcPoint.cxx
cp BmnZdc_FHCal.h BmnZdc.h
cp BmnZdc_FHCal.cxx BmnZdc.cxx

cd ../build

make

==============================

Files with FHCal geometry:
bmnroot/macro/geometry/create_rootgeom_zdc_oldnames_CBM_20mods_NICA_34mods_54mods_hole_v1.C
bmnroot/geometry/zdc_oldnames_CBM_20mods_NICA_34mods_54mods_hole_Zpos_878.1cm_Xshift_49.50cm_Yshift_0.0cm_rotationY_0.0deg_v1.root

Files with nZDC geometry:
bmnroot/macro/geometry/create_rootgeom_zdc_oldnames_NICA_36mods_no_hole_v1.C
bmnroot/geometry/zdc_oldnames_NICA_36mods_no_hole_Zpos_878.0cm_Xshift_-20.0cm_Yshift_0.0cm_rotationY_0.0deg_v1.root

In file 
bmnroot/macro/geometry/README_geom_FHCal_Hodo_ScWall_ZDC_36mods

one can find the examples how to create geometry .root files from .C files
